  "task": {
    "task_id": "202605132134-ZD2J9D",
    "title": "Hide non-actionable group roots in generated CLI docs (issue #3656)",
    "intent": "GitHub issue: https://github.com/basilisk-labs/agentplane/issues/3656\n\nSummary: generated user CLI reference includes group roots when dispatcher arg is optional but not variadic (e.g. task doc / task verify).\n\nAcceptance criteria (from issue):\n- Non-variadic optional subcommand dispatchers are classified as group roots when they have child commands.\n- Generated user CLI reference excludes those roots while preserving actionable child commands.\n- Regression coverage includes at least one non-variadic dispatcher such as task doc or task verify.\n\nPointers: packages/agentplane/src/cli/spec/docs-render.ts; review discussion linked in issue.",
    "requested_by": {
      "type": "agentplane_role",
      "id": "ORCHESTRATOR"
    }
  },
